how long do I got?

14
00:02:15,435 --> 00:02:18,370
No rush. Finish your drink.

15
00:03:45,558 --> 00:03:48,254
- Hey, Enrique.
- Chris, how are you?

16
00:03:48,361 --> 00:03:50,454
- Carlos.
- Hey, Chris, what's up?

17
00:03:50,563 --> 00:03:52,258
I got you guys set up
right back here.

18
00:03:53,733 --> 00:03:55,997
Here you go. VIP.
Anything you need, let me know.

19
00:03:56,102 --> 00:03:57,831
