don't like peanuts.

26
00:04:55,895 --> 00:04:57,487
Why not?

27
00:04:57,597 --> 00:04:59,189
They don't have any class.

28
00:04:59,299 --> 00:05:00,266
Oh, boy.

29
00:05:01,301 --> 00:05:02,563
I like 'em.

30
00:05:04,704 --> 00:05:06,934
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

31
00:05:08,274 --> 00:05:09,571
Tell me somethin'.

32
00:05:09,676 --> 00:05:11,769
What's a guy gotta do
to get a job around here?

33
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,079
Try tipping the bartender.

34
00:05:16,416 --> 00:05:17,644
Come on. I'm serious.

35
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:21,082
Sometimes they need people
at the door.

36
00:05:21,187 --> 00:05:22,654
- Oh, yeah?
- Yeah.

37
00:05:36,436 --> 00:05:38,097
Excuse me, ladies.

38
00:05:39,472 --> 00:05:40,439
Come on.

39
00:05:46,212 --> 00:05:48,077
Okay, okay. No more in the club.

40
00:05:48,181 --> 00:05:49,409
Sit down.

41
00:05:49,515 --> 00:05:51,107
That's not good enough.

42
00:05:51,718 --> 00:05:53,709
<i>Sometimes I think
you're such a prude.</i>

43
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:54,912
You know what?

44
00:05:55,021 --> 00:05:57,922
You're no good to me
with your nose full, all right?

45
00:05:58,024 --> 00:06:00,993
Plus, I promised your father.
You're my business partner.

46
00:06:01,094 --> 00:06:03,085
People come here to party.

47
00:06:03,196 --> 00:06:06,222
I don't need you to tell me
why people come here.

48
00:06:07,467 --> 00:06:10,595
Okay? I don't need trouble.
Trouble costs me money.

49
00:06:10,703 --> 00:06:12,728
- Do you understand?
- Yes.

50
00:06:21,848 --> 00:06:24,544
We're gonna have to start
stacking 'em on top of each other

51
00:06:24,650 --> 00:06:25,878
if we don't get any bigger.

52
00:06:25,985 --> 00:06:26,952
All right.

53
00:06:33,493 --> 00:06:34,721
Bigger.

54
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:55,800
I know, sweetheart...
the coke ain't yours.

55
00:07:55,908 --> 00:07:57,239
Keep your hands on the car.

56
00:07:57,343 --> 00:07:59,004
Tango Six, we're on scene.

57
00:08:01,747 --> 00:08:03,078
Let me see your I.D.

58
