couldn't save us.

61
00:08:30,176 --> 00:08:31,768
- Good evenin', Mr. Troiano.
- Andy.

62
00:09:42,281 --> 00:09:43,248
Enrique.

63
00:09:46,285 --> 00:09:48,412
- Hey, you look great, man.
- Yeah, you too.

64
00:10:00,199 --> 00:10:03,828
Donatella.
You look fabulous tonight.

65
00:10:05,037 --> 00:10:06,470
<i>Chris, mi amigo.</i>

66
00:10:06,572 --> 00:10:09,507
Signor Versace, you don't look
half bad yourself.

67
00:10:09,609 --> 00:10:11,008
Welcome to Liquid.

68
00:10:13,045 --> 00:10:14,273
How we doin' tonight?

69
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:16,177
we'd do better if we raised the cover.

70
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:18,250
Well, let's not get greedy.

71
00:10:19,285 --> 00:10:20,843
Just an idea. You're the boss.

72
00:10:20,953 --> 00:10:23,444
We want to keep the money
coming in, not going out.

73
00:10:27,727 --> 00:10:29,592
Chris, look. It's so cool.

74
00:10:29,695 --> 00:10:31,663
What is this?

75
00:10:31,764 --> 00:10:33,129
It's called publicity.

76
00:10:33,232 --> 00:10:34,961
People come here to see celebrities

77
00:10:35,067 --> 00:10:37,592
and bitchy socialites like you, not me.

78
00:10:37,703 --> 00:10:40,831
It's all about South Beach
six months after we opened up Liquid...

79
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:43,500
building boom, real estate boom,
tourism boom.

80
00:10:43,609 --> 00:10:45,099
Honey, in this town...

81
00:10:45,711 --> 00:10:47,178
you're the star.

82
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:49,213
You're dangerous and mysterious,

83
00:10:49,315 --> 00:10:51,374
and people want to know
more about you.

84
00:10:51,484 --> 00:10:52,883
Get this outta here.

85
00:11:01,994 --> 00:11:03,859
Madonna! Madonna!

86
00:11:11,771 --> 00:11:14,467
Yo, man! what the hell is this, bro?

87
00:11:14,573 --> 00:11:16,541
You gonna let everybody in but us?

88
00:11:16,642 --> 00:11:18,837
Damn right, with an attitude like that.

89
00:11:18,944 --> 00:11:21,504
This is bullshit!
I've been here for 45 minutes!

90
00:11:36,595 --> 00:11:38,187
Ciao, Sandra.

91
00:11:38,297 --> 00:11:39,958
- Oh, beautiful.
- How are ya?

92
00:11:40,066 --> 00:11:42,660
You look nice, baby.

93
00:11:55,915 --> 00:11:56,882
Come here.

94
00:12:04,356 --> 00:12:06,756
- Now what?
- what's that around your neck?

95
00:12:06,859 --> 00:12:08,486
- This thing?
- Yeah.

96
00:12:08,594 --> 00:12:11,256
- It's new jewelry.
- I thought we talked about this.

97
00:12:13,199 --> 00:12:14,598
Stop it. Stop it!

98
00:12:18,537 --> 00:12:21,267
- Mr. Troiano.
- Andy, it's "Chris. "

99
00:12:21,373 --> 00:12:24,342
