hear anything like that until tonight.

249
00:23:52,631 --> 00:23:55,566
You're talking about losing
a lot of money on account of a rumor.

250
00:23:55,667 --> 00:23:57,464
I think it's bullshit.

251
00:23:57,569 --> 00:23:58,536
