is part of the payment.

634
00:51:41,531 --> 00:51:43,658
- what about the Allie Boy sit-down?
- what about it?

635
00:51:43,767 --> 00:51:45,428
I didn't know Allie Boy was on the boat,

636
00:51:45,535 --> 00:51:48,003
and you know damn well
I got pinched as soon as I got off.

637
00:51:51,541 --> 00:51:53,270
You know what I think?

638
00:51:53,376 --> 00:51:55,606
Maybe you're getting
to like the life too much...

639
00:51:55,712 --> 00:51:59,307
the cars, the boats,
the broads, the booze.

640
00:51:59,416 --> 00:52:01,976
Look, Mike, you knew this thing
was gonna take time.

641
00:52:02,085 --> 00:52:03,575
